Hence, there are \(6\times 2=12\) different ways in which, Sabnam can carry these items to school. If we name the 2 school bags as B\({}_{{}_{1}}\), B\({}_{{}_{2}}\), the three tiffin boxes as T\({}_{{}_{1}}\), T\({}_{{}_{2}}\), T\({}_{{}_{3}}\) and the two water bottles as W\({}_{{}_{1}}\), W\({}_{{}_{2}}\), these possibilities can be illustrated in the Fig. 6.2.

