\[\overline{\text{AC}}=\overline{\text{AD}}+\overline{\text{DC}}=\bar{b}+\bar{a}\]

Hence \(\bar{a}+\bar{b}=\bar{b}+\bar{a}\)

**Property** **2** For any three vectors \(a,b\) and \(\bar{c}\)

